  "description": "Warm-season annual fruiting crop (Capsicum annuum, 60–90 days to first fruit). Includes sweet bell peppers and chili peppers (wide Scoville range 0–200,000+ SHU). Requires warm soil and air (germination \u003e70°F optimal). Slow to establish; start indoors 8–10 weeks before last frost. Heat-demanding; production slows below 20°C. Self-compatible but benefits from insect pollination. Moderate water and fertilizer needs.",
